org.neuroph.contrib.neat.gen.persistence
Interface Persistence

All Known Implementing Classes:
DirectoryOutputPersistence, NoOpPersistence
public interface Persistence

Interface defining operations that must be performed to be able to persist a Generation. The mechanism used to persist items associated with the NEAT engine is abstracted behind this interface.

Author:
Aidan Morgan
